Give users the permissions that they need to swarm on a record in Lightning Experience. Assign the Slack Service User permission set, which includes access to swarming in Slack, or create a permission set with the required permissions.

Assign users access to the Swarm Members and Swarms objects at the profile level.
From Setup, enter Profiles, select Profiles, select the user profile, click Edit, and enable Standard Object Permissions for Swarms and Swarm Members.
Repeat for other user profiles as needed.
Assign users the Slack Service User permission set or the custom permission set.
